{"tid":1966101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台調查局：中国5毛假冒台灣網友攻擊譚德塞","createTime":"2020-04-10T03:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T03:32:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d9001091b3a7d3db11c943abc8cda5ea9f1ca545","tid":1966101,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:10:58.000Z","msg":"在台北，法務部調查局表示，查獲大陸網軍假冒台灣網民攻擊世界衛生組織總幹事譚德塞，將於今日稍後召開記者會說明。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞早前在世衛日內瓦總部的例行記者會上，指責台灣過去3個月對他人身攻擊。台灣的外交部門提出嚴正抗議，要求譚德塞立即更正毫無依據的指控並道歉。蔡英文總統亦對於台灣被指控發動種族歧視攻擊的言論，表達強烈抗議。她說，計劃邀請譚德塞訪問台灣，感受台灣人民如何努力在遭受歧視和孤立之中，堅持走向世界、貢獻國際社會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519978-20200410.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519978-20200410.htm&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi62yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=d7fd601e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519978-20200410.htm&h=bc46a4c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519978-20200410.htm</a>"},{"pid":"95a3e885613aa9cceef5d1c563a1f20c2e89b83e","tid":1966101,"uid":40763,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:16:09.000Z","msg":"個迴力鏢中撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n譚：原來係boss it&rsquo;s okay"},{"pid":"a0cc54dc681c4926a21d6e60f844be07491eecac","tid":1966101,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:16:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"742250e629c992e5687bf5ebaf8e9127c56f3a59","tid":1966101,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:17:48.000Z","msg":"咁似連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/g